  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Tales of the Forgotten is a first-person walking simulator horror game with PSX-style graphics. Experience a collection of three short stories about ghosts that haunt everyday locations. Jump scares and creepy moments lurk around every corner. Each story has multiple endings to unlock. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The total playthrough time is 45-60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story 1: Mirror, Mirror</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You’ve just purchased your first house, and you can’t wait to settle in. Unfortunately, an unwelcome presence is turning your dream home into a nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/d03d6e9adbb84341deb4db04cf2aa747.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/d03d6e9adbb84341deb4db04cf2aa747.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/d03d6e9adbb84341deb4db04cf2aa747.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story 2: Laundry Night</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/70e218a1876a1d62f0fbd03885dd9dad.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/70e218a1876a1d62f0fbd03885dd9dad.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/70e218a1876a1d62f0fbd03885dd9dad.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>It’s late at night and you’re washing your clothes in a laundromat alone. Or at least, you think you’re alone, until you suddenly become aware of a ghost who is asking for your help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/9d942cb93983cc52522369c1a29e0287.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/9d942cb93983cc52522369c1a29e0287.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/9d942cb93983cc52522369c1a29e0287.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story 3: Unfinished Business</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're working the night shift as a janitor in a seemingly empty sales office. As the night continues, it becomes clear that multiple ghostly presences have joined you for the evening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/3c9d0a991960f1c80f45eeb3d19bd0ef.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/3c9d0a991960f1c80f45eeb3d19bd0ef.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/3c9d0a991960f1c80f45eeb3d19bd0ef.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each of the three stories has multiple endings to explore and unlock.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Tales of the Forgotten is a first-person walking simulator horror game with PSX-style graphics. Experience a collection of three short stories about ghosts that haunt everyday locations. Jump scares and creepy moments lurk around every corner. Each story has multiple endings to unlock. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The total playthrough time is 45-60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story 1: Mirror, Mirror</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You’ve just purchased your first house, and you can’t wait to settle in. Unfortunately, an unwelcome presence is turning your dream home into a nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn