e_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/9d942cb93983cc52522369c1a29e0287.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story 3: Unfinished Business</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're working the night shift as a janitor in a seemingly empty sales office. As the night continues, it becomes clear that multiple ghostly presences have joined you for the evening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/3c9d0a991960f1c80f45eeb3d